--Made by Stickmasterluke
sp=script.Parent
firerate=4 range=100 power=300 rate=1/30 barreloffset=Vector3.new(0,0,-1.5) windvec=Vector3.new(2,-1,1).unit
debris=game:GetService("Debris") equipped=false check=true
function waitfor(parent,name) while parent:FindFirstChild(name)==nil do wait() end return parent:FindFirstChild(name) end
local storeWeld=waitfor(sp,"BoltWeld")
function checkintangible(hit) if hit and hit~=nil then if hit:IsDescendantOf(sp.Parent) or hit.Transparency>.8 or hit.Name=="Handle" or hit.Name=="Effect" or hit.Name=="Bullet" or hit.Name=="Laser" or string.lower(hit.Name)=="water" or hit.Name=="Rail" or hit.Name=="Arrow" then return true end end return false end
function castray(startpos,vec,length,ignore,delayifhit) local hit,endpos2=game.Workspace:FindPartOnRay(Ray.new(startpos,vec*length),ignore) if hit~=nil then if checkintangible(hit) then if delayifhit then wait() end hit,endpos2=castray(endpos2+(vec*.01),vec,length-((startpos-endpos2).magnitude),ignore,delayifhit) end end return hit,endpos2 end
function drawbeam(beamstart,beamend,clr,fadedelay) local dist=(beamstart-beamend).magnitude local laser=Instance.new("Part") laser.Name="Effect" laser.Anchored=true laser.CanCollide=false laser.Shape="Block" laser.formFactor="Custom" laser.Size=Vector3.new(.2,.2,.2) laser.Transparency=5 laser.Material=Enum.Material.Plastic laser.Locked=true laser.TopSurface=0 laser.BottomSurface=0 laser.BrickColor=clr laser.CFrame=CFrame.new(beamend,beamstart)*CFrame.new(0,0,-dist/2)*CFrame.Angles(math.pi/2,0,0) local m=Instance.new("SpecialMesh") m.Scale=Vector3.new(1,dist*5,1) m.Parent=laser debris:AddItem(laser,fadedelay*3) laser.Parent=game.Workspace
local frames=math.floor(fadedelay/rate) for frame=1,frames do wait(rate) local percent=frame/frames laser.CFrame=laser.CFrame+windvec*rate laser.Transparency=.5+(percent*.5) end wait(1) laser:remove() end
function onEquipped(mouse) equipped=true if mouse~=nil then mouse.Icon="rbxasset://textures\\GunCursor.png" mouse.Button1Down:connect(function() local hu=sp.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") local he=sp.Parent:FindFirstChild("Head") local t=sp.Parent:FindFirstChild("Torso") if check and hu and hu.Health>0 and t and he then check=false
local startpos=he.Position local fakestartpos=(sp.Handle.CFrame*CFrame.new(barreloffset)).p local vec=(mouse.Hit.p-startpos).unit
local p=Instance.new("Part") p.Name="Arrow" p.Locked=true p.BrickColor=BrickColor.new("Black") p.TopSurface="Smooth" p.BottomSurface="Smooth" p.formFactor="Custom" p.Size=Vector3.new(.3,.3,1.25) local m=Instance.new("SpecialMesh") m.MeshId="http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=101708120" m.TextureId="http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=101707733" m.Scale=Vector3.new(1,1,1.618) m.Parent=p
local c=Instance.new("ObjectValue") c.Name="creator" c.Value=game.Players.LocalPlayer c.Parent=p
local sound=Instance.new("Sound") sound.SoundId="http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=16211030" sound.Volume=1 sound.Parent=p sound:Play()
local s=script.Script:clone() s.Parent=p s.Disabled=false
local hit,endpos=castray(startpos,vec,range,sp.Parent,false) local fakevec=(endpos-fakestartpos).unit if hit~=nil then local newcf=CFrame.new(endpos,endpos+fakevec)*CFrame.new(0,0,.5) p.CFrame=newcf local w=Instance.new("Weld") w.Part0=hit w.Part1=p w.C0=hit.CFrame:inverse()*newcf w.C1=newcf:inverse()*newcf w.Parent=p p.CanCollide=false else p.CFrame=CFrame.new(endpos,endpos+fakevec) p.Velocity=fakevec*power p.Parent=game.Workspace end
local f=Instance.new("Fire") f.Heat=10 f.Size=.5 f.Parent=p
debris:AddItem(p,20) p.Parent=game.Workspace
delay(0,function() drawbeam(fakestartpos,endpos,BrickColor.new("Institutional white"),.25) end)
local firesound=sp.Handle:FindFirstChild("FireSound") if firesound~=nil then firesound:Play() end local shoulder=t:FindFirstChild("Right Shoulder") if shoulder~=nil then shoulder.CurrentAngle=2 end if sp:FindFirstChild("Handle2") then sp.Handle2.Transparency=1 end mouse.Icon="rbxasset://textures\\GunWaitCursor.png" wait(firerate) if sp:FindFirstChild("Handle2") then sp.Handle2.Transparency=0 end mouse.Icon="rbxasset://textures\\GunCursor.png" check=true end end) end if storeWeld then storeWeld.Parent=sp end end
function onUnequipped() equipped=false end
sp.Equipped:connect(onEquipped) sp.Unequipped:connect(onUnequipped)

--Stickmasterluke
sp=script.Parent
damage=19
poisondamage=46 poisontime=7
wait()
local weld=sp:FindFirstChild("Weld") if weld~=nil then if weld.Part0~=nil then hit=weld.Part0 local sound=sp:FindFirstChild("Sound") if sound~=nil then sound:Play() end local ct=sp:FindFirstChild("creator") if ct.Value~=nil and ct.Value.Character~=nil then if hit.Parent~=ct.Value.Character and hit.Name~="Handle" and hit.Name~="Effect" then local h=hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") local t=hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Torso") if h~=nil and t~=nil and h.Health>0 then for i,v in ipairs(h:GetChildren()) do if v.Name=="creator" then v:remove() end end ct:clone().Parent=h h:TakeDamage(damage) end end end local stingspersecond=1 local stings=poisontime*stingspersecond for i=1,stings do wait(1/stingspersecond) local ct=sp:FindFirstChild("creator") if ct.Value~=nil and ct.Value.Character~=nil then if hit.Parent~=ct.Value.Character and hit.Name~="Handle" and hit.Name~="Effect" then local h=hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") local t=hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Torso") if h~=nil and t~=nil and h.Health>0 then for i,v in ipairs(h:GetChildren()) do if v.Name=="creator" then v:remove() end end ct:clone().Parent=h h:TakeDamage(poisondamage/stings) end end end end local f=sp:FindFirstChild("Fire") if f~=nil then f.Enabled=false end end else sp.Touched:connect(function(hit) if hit~=nil and not check then local ct=sp:FindFirstChild("creator") if ct.Value~=nil and ct.Value.Character~=nil then if hit.Parent~=ct.Value.Character and hit.Name~="Handle" and hit.Name~="Effect" then check=true local h=hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") local t=hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Torso") if h~=nil and t~=nil and h.Health>0 then for i,v in ipairs(h:GetChildren()) do if v.Name=="creator" then v:remove() end end ct:clone().Parent=h h:TakeDamage(damage) end end end end end) end
